5
One Move Captures Black (25)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par This is an easy problem.
\par
\par There are not many places to play so please read thoroughly and do not make any mistakes.
\par
\par The first move is the key.
\par }
